49
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:22,960
Yebin is always protecting us quietly.

50
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,930
Minah also

51
00:03:25,579 --> 00:03:28,470
works very hard.

52
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:32,420
I'm also very happy

53
00:03:32,890 --> 00:03:35,360
to be able to join Wonder-X.

54
00:03:36,570 --> 00:03:39,460
No matter what happens,

55
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:41,520
