75
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:44,130
We're just ordinary girls.

76
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:46,470
But we keep living in bad comments.

77
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,750
Those who are watching this,

78
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:52,409
think about

79
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:54,470
