96
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,020
More importantly,

97
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:42,280
I just want you to be happy.

98
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,140
It's great

99
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:48,980
