100
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:54,420
Let's go.

101
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,370
We have to go to the company.

102
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:14,800
Hello.

103
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,430
Get in the car first.

104
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:21,970
Thank you.

105
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,100
