106
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,659
Let me put a blanket on you.

107
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:49,770
The heater is on.

108
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:53,380
Bin.

109
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,060
Mm?

110
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,400
Thank you for today.

111
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:02,530
If it weren't for you,
something bad would've happened.

112
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:07,580
The person who wrote that question
was the one in the wrong.

113
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:11,520
You were really cool today.

114
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:13,990
I almost fell for you.

115
00:09:16,170 --> 00:09:16,830
I'm also

116
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:19,940
really happy to be on a show with you.

117
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,000
Your hands are cold.

118
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,950
Is it better now?

119
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,160
Yes.

120
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:39,770
It's nice.

121
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,160
Ji-eun.

122
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,340
Can I kiss you?

123
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:39,650
Ji-eun.

124
00:10:40,450 --> 00:10:43,080
I've always wanted to say this.

125
00:10:45,810 --> 00:10:47,780
You've worked hard

126
00:10:49,190 --> 00:10:51,120
